# --- recruiter-facing public tree -----------------------------------------
# These paths remain on disk as local experiment history, but are intentionally
# absent from the public Git index. Exceptions below are the compact evidence
# and canonical entry points retained on the default branch.
/v3/CLAUDE.md
/v3/实验方案.md
/v3/shared/eval_log.jsonl

/v3/E1_baseline/eval/*
!/v3/E1_baseline/eval/03_eval_pass_at_k.py
/v3/E1_baseline/outputs/
/v3/E1_baseline/tools/*
!/v3/E1_baseline/tools/_compute_pass_maj_curves.py
!/v3/E1_baseline/tools/_make_difficulty_labels.py

/v3/E2_sft/FINDINGS.md
/v3/E2_sft/eval/
